title: Was a Woman Caught Smuggling Nearly 1,000 Cacti and Succulents Strapped to Her Body?
subtitle: The booty was reportedly worth an estimated $10,000 in local currency.
author: Madison Dapcevich
vclaim: A New Zealand woman was sentenced to a year of “intensive supervision” after attempting to smuggle 947 succulents and cacti strapped to her body in 2019.
